metadata.name: Unravel
metadata.description:
Definition of Unravel:

To undo (twisted, knitted, or woven threads)
Investigate and solve or explain (something complicated or puzzling).

"they were attempting to unravel the cause of death"

This is what life is like alongside The Body.  The Mind doesn't always cohesively exist well, with check-ins and the proverbial "hello" of a long-time friend, the body.
